   ``It seems like everybody's in a good mood despite the heat. I
haven't seen a crabby face yet.'' _ Paula Torres, watching a
festive crowd of baseball fans gather near Wrigley Field in
99-degree heat, in anticipation of the first night game at the
field in its 74-year history.
