<FILEID>AP-NR-08-09-88 0614EDT</FILEID>
<1ST_LINE>a e BC-WKD--Herman Adv19-21   08-09 0939</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>BC-WKD--Herman, Adv 19-21,0960</2ND_LINE>
